AscendOS — Licensing
====================

This repository currently contains design documentation only (no source code).

Documentation and design content
--------------------------------
All documentation, diagrams, and design content in this repository are licensed
under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).

You are free to share and adapt the material for any purpose, including
commercially, provided you give appropriate credit.

Full text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

Future source code
------------------
When source code is added, it is intended to be dual-licensed under your choice
of:

    MIT OR Apache-2.0

This is the prevailing convention in the systems/Rust community: MIT for
simplicity, Apache-2.0 for its explicit patent grant. The intent is stated here
in advance so that contributors understand the terms before any code exists.
This section is informational until the first code lands, at which point the
relevant LICENSE-MIT and LICENSE-APACHE files will be added.

SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-4.0
